  "description_jsonb": {
	"zh": "[Everything Claude Code](https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code) 是由 Anthropic x Forum Ventures 黑客松冠军 Affaan Mustafa 历经 10 个月日常实战沉淀后开源的 [Claude Code](https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code) 配置增强层。它并非独立软件，而是一套精心设计的「四层架构」插件体系——覆盖 13 个专属智能体、40+ 按需技能模块、32 条快捷指令，以及业界罕见的跨会话持续学习系统（v1/v2 双引擎）。借助 AgentShield 的 912 条安全规则扫描与分层委派模型，开发者可将原本需要手动触发的代码审查、TDD 引导、构建错误修复等工作流完全自动化，使 Claude Code 真正进化为可信赖的「AI 团队成员」，而非单纯的聊天式代码生成器。项目已在 GitHub 积累近 5 万 Star，并发布至 Claude Code 插件市场，支持 TypeScript、Python、Go、Java、C++ 五种主流语言的差异化规则配置。",
	"en": "[Everything Claude Code](https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code) is a production-hardened configuration enhancement layer for [Claude Code](https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code), open-sourced by Anthropic hackathon winner Affaan Mustafa after 10+ months of daily use. Rather than a standalone tool, it is a meticulously architected four-layer plugin system comprising 13 specialized agents, 40+ on-demand skill modules, 32 shortcut commands, and a cross-session continuous learning engine (v1 skill-based + v2 instinct-based). AgentShield delivers 912-rule security scanning, while a hierarchical delegation model ensures each agent only accesses tools within its defined scope. Workflows like code review, TDD guidance, and build-error resolution — previously requiring manual triggers — become fully automated. With nearly 50k GitHub stars and availability on the Claude Code plugin marketplace, the project supports differentiated rule configurations for TypeScript, Python, Go, Java, and C++."
